title: 02/01/21 DPS Hour 1 Albert Breer
itunes:title: 02/01/21 DPS Hour 1 Albert Breer
description:
Albert Breer tells Dan that he could tell that Stafford was about to be traded because he heard that teams had shown a real interest in trading for him. Albert says that Goff's contract made him have to be included in the trade.
